{"tid":1409634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［認真］［前線一定要睇］我哋會捉住啲狗 然後","createTime":"2019-08-04T23:09:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T05:24:52.000Z","uid":233118,"like":64,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5645755bbf842dc49b2fecbebf631aa3d46fc896","tid":1409634,"uid":233118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T23:09:10.000Z","msg":"我知大家好嬲<br />\n<br />\n但今日有和理非在場<br />\n<br />\n所以盡量唔好有死人重傷事件出現<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">衝 一定嘅</span><br />\n<br />\n問題喺衝完點對付啲狗<br />\n<br />\n制服在地，解除武裝喺一定<br />\n<br />\n然後個人建議（順序）<br />\n<br />\n1.綁起手腳<br />\n<br />\n2. 5~10人為一組看管（方便看管）<br />\n<br />\n3.遊街示眾（侮辱）<br />\n<br />\n4.揼比和理非教化（減輕前線壓力+侮辱+團結和理非）<br />\n<br />\n5.囚禁一定時數後要求家人保釋（交錢支援抗爭+極大侮辱）（建議範圍200~2000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n至少比基本人權，eg 食水，醫療<br />\n<br />\n唔好位俾人入<br />\n<br />\n至於武力使用<br />\n<br />\n唔好打死or重傷<br />\n<br />\n但遇到反抗嘅大力少少冇人會介意嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5605bf1cb7e55f064e27dd5f79185c6f2d30d2a7","tid":1409634,"uid":233118,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T23:09:27.000Z","msg":"起身啦"},{"pid":"63235b361ae8d175b96ccde5cf43337fb18e38c5","tid":1409634,"uid":233118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T23:09:40.000Z","msg":"睇吓點對啲狗"},{"pid":"b5ced7f96588870f409c7d151ba46e5c5416fe79","tid":1409634,"uid":233118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T23:09:52.000Z","msg":"推俾所有人睇"},{"pid":"91a2431a988645764d2d81673ce3340cbee56cd6","tid":1409634,"uid":233118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T23:10:16.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0884c38b425565ad3852ae34339c62356d37e118","tid":1409634,"uid":233118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T23:11:36.000Z","msg":"記住以武制暴"},{"pid":"53361d62b5235ccff0384b49c6aea69efda2cbcd","tid":1409634,"uid":233118,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T23:11:50.000Z","msg":"我要hit and run"},{"pid":"6131f2a34c59e95d6d16618d1b6b1d84459fc438","tid":1409634,"uid":166245,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T23:12:06.000Z","msg":"收錢保釋果度要諗下<br />\n好似會比人一種敲詐感覺"},{"pid":"84f75377b1d6b0cb3cc6bff77aa01b30cdab88c7","tid":1409634,"uid":233118,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T23:12:13.000Z","msg":"唔好俾五毛分化"},{"pid":"192203891f00fbbaaa4bacf7755d607896395a36","tid":1409634,"uid":233118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6131f2a34c59e95d6d16618d1b6b1d84459fc438","tid":1409634,"uid":166245,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T23:12:06.000Z","msg":"收錢保釋果度要諗下<br />\n好似會比人一種敲詐感覺"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T23:14:24.000Z","msg":"建議<br />\n<br />\n但前線物資好短缺<br />\n<br />\n同埋和理非同記者有監管就可以<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有咩比向警犬收保釋更加侮辱</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"334c268162b05449ea5a084b46d0769542f69455","tid":1409634,"uid":233118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T23:15:22.000Z","msg":"漏咗<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">影低所有警犬+number<br />\n<br />\n建立data base</span></span>"},{"pid":"c8edfac6db165b3348b86764bffd2b76c3a7899d","tid":1409634,"uid":233118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T23:15:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ab34f777328473cb159d88b7567252dbc1664f2a","tid":1409634,"uid":233118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T23:16:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">影低所有警犬+number<br />\n<br />\n建立data base</span></span>"},{"pid":"0fe7d3fbc4915cfa72c14a8e02d9325581551cfb","tid":1409634,"uid":233118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T23:16:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-si